415
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:16,520
Did you not know any of it?

416
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:20,930
I... didn't know.

417
00:42:23,450 --> 00:42:26,350
If His Imperial Majesty found out about this,

418
00:42:26,350 --> 00:42:29,850
a light punishment includes penalties for you and Prince Rong,

419
00:42:29,850 --> 00:42:34,530
a serious punishment includes you being demoted to a commoner and Prince Rong being exiled out of the capital.

420
00:42:35,950 --> 00:42:39,650
Who knows what His Majesty will do?

421
00:42:39,650 --> 00:42:43,420
He can even bestow death upon the late crown prince without hesitation.

422
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:48,090
Do you think he will let anything pass by this time？

423
00:42:52,790 --> 00:42:56,980
Prince Rong is finally valued by His Majesty.

424
00:42:56,980 --> 00:42:58,990
But now it may...

